  "purpose": "The Arkansas Citizens United Coalition is the statewide organizational backbone of the Citizens United Education Platform. While the website educates individuals, ACUCOS connects organizations, institutions, and community leaders into a coordinated educational network.",
  "governing_principle": "The Arkansas Citizens United Coalition exists to strengthen civic education through partnership. Success is measured not by organizational size or influence, but by the coalition's ability to help more Arkansans understand Citizens United, engage thoughtfully with reliable information, and share that knowledge within their own communities.",
  "coalition_vision": "Establish at least one active educational partner in every Arkansas county. Each partner contributes according to its mission, capacity, and expertise while maintaining organizational independence. Amplify civic education through collaboration rather than centralization.",
